<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132"><strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="132">Delivery address description</strong> – The delivery address of the sales order</li>
</ul>
<p sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="134">For items, the following columns are required:</p>
<ul sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136">
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136"><strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="136">Product</strong> – The product to order</li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137"><strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="137">Quantity</strong> – The quantity of the selected product</li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138"><strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">Unit</strong> – The unit of measure (for example, <strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">ea.</strong>, <strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">kgs</strong>, or <strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="138">box</strong>)</li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="139"><strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="139">Ship to country/region</strong> – The country or region of delivery</li>
