</ul>
<p sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="142">You must make sure that your Customer portal somehow submits values for all these columns.</p>
<p sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="144">If you want to add columns to the page, or remove columns, see <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/dynamics365/customerengagement/on-premises/customize/create-edit-quick-create-forms" sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="144">Create or edit quick create forms for a streamlined data entry experience</a>.</p>
