<h2 id="customize-the-home-page" sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="151">Customize the home page</h2>
<p sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="153">All the controls in the Customer portal are built-in Power Apps portals controls. You can customize them by following the steps in <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/powerapps/maker/portals/compose-page" sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="153">Compose a page</a> in the Power Apps portals documentation.</p>
