</li>
<li sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="162"><p sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="162">In the navigation pane on the left, select <strong sourcefile="supply-chain/sales-marketing/customer-portal-customize.md" sourcestartlinenumber="162">Page Templates</strong>.</p>
